node.text: Hey guys! These challenging times around the world have made us want to connect with all of you so much. They have also made us want to stay connected with each other. We got inspired to record and sing together again seeing how many smiles our check in video created weeks back. We spent some time recently recording one of our favorite songs (safely apart) and wanted to share it with you all as our small way of saying thank you. We are sending love to all of you WORLDWIDE. Please take care of yourselves, take care of each other and take care of all of your fellow neighbors. We’ll be thinking about you 😀 @bigtimerush @loganhenderson @kendallschmidt @therealcarlospena

node.text: Our foster dog Blu and so many other animals need your help! These rescues like @realgood.dog rely on the kindness and generosity of people like you so if you can please donate and save a life. Either way please share this message! Thank you thank you. We love you guys! DONATE: http://paypal.me/realgoodrescue

node.title: Please watch and share! @caitlinsheyspears @realgood.dog and I need you!

node.text: Cheers to my freaking birthday weekend! 🥳 It is weird to wish myself a happy birthday? No. It would be weird if I didn’t want me to have a happy birthday. So here we go.
